            <title>更远、更实用，五菱之光 EV 305km 进取型上市，售价 5.78 万元</title>
        
    <link>https://www.ifanr.com/1631830?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=</link>
    <comments>https://www.ifanr.com/1631830?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=#comments</comments>
    <pubDate>Thu, 24 Jul 2025 15:21:59 +0000</pubDate>
