          <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1631879" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/QCULTRAII301066.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/QCULTRAII301066.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/QCULTRAII301066-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/QCULTRAII301066-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/QCULTRAII301066-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>在旗舰定位开放式真无线耳机 BOSE Ultra 推出了大概一年后，BOSE 用个相同的名字做了一款全新的入耳式真无线降噪耳机。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1631879" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/QCULTRAII301066.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/QCULTRAII301066.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/QCULTRAII301066-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/QCULTRAII301066-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/QCULTRAII301066-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>这款新品延续了 QC 系列「大鲨」的定位，改用 BOSE Ultra 系列全新的设计，加入了空间音频支持和智能耳内音场调校技术，还有标志性的降噪性能，是 BOSE 新一代旗舰级的真无线降噪耳机。</p>
<p>2299 的定价，似乎还比之前低一点。</p>
<h3>ULTRA 风格的外观</h3>
<p>不管是开放式还是入耳式降噪，两款耳机的充电盒都采用非常相似的椭圆设计。基于耳机是纵向收纳在充电盒内侧，入耳降噪的 BOSE ULTRA 充电盒会比开放式用的长不少。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631880 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/01QCULTRAII301085.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/01QCULTRAII301085.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/01QCULTRAII301085-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/01QCULTRAII301085-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/01QCULTRAII301085-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>充电盒的表面加入消光磨砂处理，正面中心只保留了 BOSE 的大 LOGO 和上方非常小的状态指示灯。充电盒内侧也有状态指示灯，上侧和正面都能够看到。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631881 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/02QCULTRAII301084.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/02QCULTRAII301084.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/02QCULTRAII301084-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/02QCULTRAII301084-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/02QCULTRAII301084-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>机身这个材质比较容易沾痕迹和指纹，日常使用建议加上保护壳。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631882 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/03QCULTRAII301082.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/03QCULTRAII301082.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/03QCULTRAII301082-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/03QCULTRAII301082-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/03QCULTRAII301082-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>基于无线充电的支持，充电盒后侧处理得很干净平整。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631883 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/04QCULTRAII301083.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/04QCULTRAII301083.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/04QCULTRAII301083-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/04QCULTRAII301083-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/04QCULTRAII301083-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>BOSE 保留了实体按键，能非常直观地快速开启配对模式，方便多设备用户进行配对。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631884 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/05QCULTRAII301091.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/05QCULTRAII301091.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/05QCULTRAII301091-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/05QCULTRAII301091-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/05QCULTRAII301091-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>耳机采用了短耳柄的入耳式设计，机身圆润饱满，对耳轮空间比较大的用户佩戴起来会比较舒服。</p>
<p>这一代也附带了 BOSE 标志性的鲨鱼鳍设计，他们用了更短、更软和更圆润的耳鳍结构，刚好能够填满耳机到对耳轮上侧的空间，佩戴就能够更加牢固。有这个结构之后，运动时佩戴都不需要担心佩戴稳固性，日常通勤和到健身房都可以用。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1631885" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/06QCULTRAII301093.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/06QCULTRAII301093.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/06QCULTRAII301093-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/06QCULTRAII301093-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/06QCULTRAII301093-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>鲨鱼鳍设计的弧形边缘足够圆滑，加上这个扁平的耳帽，耳机入耳的感觉很舒服，没有明显受力点，不容易累。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631886 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/07QCULTRAII301087.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/07QCULTRAII301087.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/07QCULTRAII301087-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/07QCULTRAII301087-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/07QCULTRAII301087-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>配色方面，BOSE 先是提供了经典黑和晨雾白两款常用配色，晨雾白是有点复古白的暖调。后续，他们还增加了和 QC ULTRA 宋雨琦联名款相同配色「绛梅紫」。</p>
<h3>更沉浸，更安静</h3>
<p>配置方面，QC Ultra II 搭载了支持蓝牙 5.3 的无线传输方案，和开放式版 QC Ultra 一样加入了高通高规格编码 aptX 的支持，最高能够实现 aptX Adaptive 的编码支持。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631887 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/08QCULTRAII301080.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1687" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/08QCULTRAII301080.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/08QCULTRAII301080-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/08QCULTRAII301080-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/08QCULTRAII301080-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>加入 aptX Adaptive 不只是为了传输规格提升，延迟的控制也是重点。Bose QC Ultra II 用来看视频和打游戏基本感觉不到延迟，连接时也没有出现断连断播的情况。</p>
<p>连接的最远距离为 9 米，如果公司里连接的是电脑，还算够用。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631888 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/09QCULTRAII301076.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1687" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/09QCULTRAII301076.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/09QCULTRAII301076-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/09QCULTRAII301076-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/09QCULTRAII301076-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>和其他 Bose 耳机一样，BOSE QC Ultra II 支持 BOSE app 的连接控制，用户操控降噪和听感，开启空间音频等操作都能在 app 上操作。</p>
<p>降噪，是这一代更新的重点。</p>
<p>BOSE QC Ultra II 搭载了 BOSE 自家的降噪技术，不管在降噪深度、降噪时的听感和耳压控制都有非常突出的表现。相较于之前更新的小鲨 2 代，BOSE QC Ultra II 降噪状态下更加干净，降噪开启后耳压控制得更好，能在保持声音安静的同时耳压也没那么明显，听起来更加舒服。</p>
<p>这一代降噪强度的提升，会更明显。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631889 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/10QCULTRAII301044.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/10QCULTRAII301044.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/10QCULTRAII301044-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/10QCULTRAII301044-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/10QCULTRAII301044-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>在室内环境中测试时，我们尝试坐在空调的正下方，让空调垂直对着自己的同时把出风量调到最大，之后再开启降噪。此时，耳机能够将全部的环境噪声全部压下来，安静得像是完全没有开空调一样。</p>
<p>另外，我们也在测试中用蓝牙音箱播放音乐，BOSE QC Ultra II 都能够将播放歌曲大部分背景声都压下来，人声部分做了一些平滑的处理，让它在背景声音降低之后听起来没那么违和、刺耳。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631890 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/11QCULTRAII301048.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1687" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/11QCULTRAII301048.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/11QCULTRAII301048-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/11QCULTRAII301048-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/11QCULTRAII301048-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>BOSE 对通透模式也做了升级，他们采用 ActiveSense 噪声动态感应技术，进一步优化通透环境中的声音表现，佩戴时依然能够听到周围环境的声音，不影响你和身边人交流。但耳机会优化环境中尖锐的声音，通透模式下也能有一种安静感。</p>
<p>实际听起来，BOSE QC Ultra II 的通透环境很顺滑舒服，大型抽湿机和空调产生的噪声都有了平滑的过渡，声音进入耳朵很真实干净，少了从麦克风出来的数码感。</p>
<p>在耳朵旁边打响指的话，耳机能够快速响应，能对突如其来的声音做调整，你会感到「突」的安静了一下，有一种突然改变成降噪模式的感觉。</p>
<p>不过声音变化会有些突兀，之后如果可以简单优化一下会更好。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631891 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/12QCULTRAII301054.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/12QCULTRAII301054.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/12QCULTRAII301054-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/12QCULTRAII301054-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/12QCULTRAII301054-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>续航部分，耳机本体的续航时间为 6 小时，支持充电 20 分钟播放两小时的快充模式，充电盒支持无线充电。</p>
<p>就单体的续航看来，BOSE QC Ultra II 相较于其他开启降噪能到 7-8 小时的旗舰耳机来说，还是弱一些。</p>
<h3>更懂你的听感</h3>
<p>除了降噪，声音也是本次的更新重点。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631892 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/13QCULTRAII301074.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/13QCULTRAII301074.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/13QCULTRAII301074-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/13QCULTRAII301074-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/13QCULTRAII301074-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>BOSE 在这一代耳机中加入了 CustomTune 智能耳内音场调校技术，可以根据佩戴者的耳朵特点进行调校音频和降噪的功能。比起还需要手动检测的耳朵版「房间检测」，BOSE 这个还要更智能一点。</p>
<p>此外，降噪模式也做了优化。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631893 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/14QCULTRAII301079.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1687" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/14QCULTRAII301079.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/14QCULTRAII301079-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/14QCULTRAII301079-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/14QCULTRAII301079-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>除了常规的降噪和环境声模式，BOSE 这次还提供了一个专属的沉浸式音频模式。它是完全消噪和沉浸空间音频的组合，常态下和常规消噪模式没有区别，开启音乐播放时就能够获得降噪和空间音频的效果。</p>
<p>用户可以通过长按耳机左侧快速切换着三个模式，不需要在进入 BOSE app 开启空间音频，操作还挺方便的。</p>
<p>还有就是，这一代支持了 aptX Adaptive 编码，比起以前只有 AAC 的同定位旧品，BOSE QC ULTRA II 可以进行更高规格的传输，声音的质量基础得到保证。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631894 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/15QCULTRAII301070.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/15QCULTRAII301070.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/15QCULTRAII301070-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/15QCULTRAII301070-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/15QCULTRAII301070-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>听感部分，QC ULTRA II 给我的第一印象就是声音很扎实。</p>
<p>低频浑厚，鼓点的边缘较为圆滑，一下一下敲下来有种很适合流行乐的饱满感。人声和背景的距离不太多，但每个部分听着依旧清晰。</p>
<p>在 aptX Adaptive 的规格提升后，歌手演唱时的呼吸声、喉底音还有周边细微的乐器声变清晰了，能够听到歌手呼吸变化过程，整体听起来也更加自然，整个声音基底要比上一代旗舰提升了不少。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631895 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/16QCULTRAII301068.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/16QCULTRAII301068.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/16QCULTRAII301068-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/16QCULTRAII301068-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/16QCULTRAII301068-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>这一点，在音源质量更高的流媒体服务上会更明显，像是可以提供无损的 Apple Music、Tidal、Qobuz 和 QQ 音乐、网易云等流媒体，足够的细节量和顺滑无需锐化就能够突出的细节表现，BOSE QC ULTRA II 的听感也更舒服。</p>
<p>听 Spotify 的话，声音有些时候有些锐化得不那么自然，数码味和味精味都被放大了，听感会有点影响。</p>
<h3>值得更新吗？</h3>
<p>整体而言，我觉得 BOSE QC ULTRA II 是非常值得升级的一代。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631896 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/17QCULTRAII301058.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/17QCULTRAII301058.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/17QCULTRAII301058-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/17QCULTRAII301058-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/17QCULTRAII301058-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>机身对佩戴做了优化，鲨鱼鳍变得更圆滑的它在保证佩戴稳定度的同时，佩戴舒适度也提高了。耳机可以兼容轻松的运动、通勤场景，不需要为了健身准备一副专门的运动耳机。</p>
<p>降噪效果有升级，比上一代「大鲨」更强，声底更干净、舒服。耳压的变化不再强势，入耳体感更舒适，戴着不那么容易累。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631897 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/18QCULTRAII301063.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="1688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/18QCULTRAII301063.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/18QCULTRAII301063-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/18QCULTRAII301063-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/18QCULTRAII301063-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>加上这个有 ActiveSense 技术加持的环境声模式，降噪和环境声的听感都被照顾到，体验完整了。</p>
<p>声音体验的升级也很大，BOSE 用一个 CustomTune 技术就能够将听感提升到另一个阶段，保证低频表现的同时降低了高频平白锐化带来的尖锐数码感，听感更贴合真实体验，听感上也有更适合大众的舒适度，听起来比之前好听了不少。</p>
<p><img class="size-full wp-image-1631898 aligncenter" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20QCULTRAII301097.jpg" alt="" width="3000" height="2000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20QCULTRAII301097.jpg 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20QCULTRAII301097-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20QCULTRAII301097-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20QCULTRAII301097-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p>
<p>加上现在比 2499 这个传统旗舰定价更低的 2299 元起售价，部分更进取的店家可做到 2100 左右的到手价，对 BOSE 用户来说可以说是非常值得更新的一款。</p>
